{"markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"","page-layout":"full","toc":false},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"page-hero\">\n  <div class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;\">\n    <p class=\"eyebrow\">About</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Anurita Sharma</h1>\n    <p style=\"color:#4A6A88;font-size:0.95rem;\">Policy Strategist · Program Manager · Georgetown University</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Bio + Skills -->\n<div class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"grid-2\" style=\"gap:2.5rem;align-items:start;\">\n    \n    <div>\n      <div class=\"hero-avatar\" style=\"margin-bottom:1rem;width:80px;height:80px;font-size:1.4rem;\">AS</div>\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.92rem;color:#2C4A66;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;\">\n        I've spent nine years at the intersection of research and action — translating evidence \n        into programs that serve real people. I started in county-level health administration, \n        moved into federal evaluation work, and now work across the public and nonprofit sectors \n        on policy strategy and program design.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.92rem;color:#2C4A66;line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1rem;\">\n        I believe the best policy work is invisible — it just looks like things finally working. \n        My approach is rigorous on the evidence side and deeply human on the implementation side.\n      </p>\n      <p style=\"font-size:0.92rem;color:#2C4A66;line-height:1.8;\">\n        At Georgetown I study public policy with a focus on program evaluation, causal inference, \n        and applied data analytics — building the methodological depth to match the field experience.\n      </p>\n    </div>\n\n    <div>\n      <div class=\"section-divider\">Skills &amp; tools</div>\n\n      <div class=\"skills-group\">\n        <div class=\"skills-group-name\">Analysis &amp; data</div>\n        <div class=\"pills-row\">\n          <span class=\"pill pill-blue\">Stata</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-blue\">R / Tidyverse</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-blue\">Python</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-blue\">ArcGIS / spmap</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-blue\">Power BI</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"skills-group\">\n        <div class=\"skills-group-name\">Evaluation &amp; causal inference</div>\n        <div class=\"pills-row\">\n          <span class=\"pill pill-sky\">RCT design</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-sky\">Monte Carlo simulation</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-sky\">DAG reasoning</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-sky\">Mixed methods</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-sky\">Power analysis</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"skills-group\">\n        <div class=\"skills-group-name\">Communication &amp; policy</div>\n        <div class=\"pills-row\">\n          <span class=\"pill pill-teal\">Policy briefs</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-teal\">Quarto / R Markdown</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-teal\">Public testimony</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-teal\">Evidence synthesis</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n\n      <div class=\"skills-group\">\n        <div class=\"skills-group-name\">Program management</div>\n        <div class=\"pills-row\">\n          <span class=\"pill pill-slate\">Federal grants</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-slate\">Budget oversight</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-slate\">Stakeholder engagement</span>\n          <span class=\"pill pill-slate\">Cross-sector partnerships</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Experience Timeline -->\n<div style=\"background:#F7FAFE;border-top:1px solid #D0DFF0;border-bottom:1px solid #D0DFF0;\">\n  <div class=\"content-section\">\n    <div class=\"section-divider\">Experience</div>\n\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n      <div class=\"tl-dot-col\"><div class=\"tl-dot\"></div><div class=\"tl-line\"></div></div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"tl-role\">MPP Candidate — Public Policy & Data Analytics</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-org\">Georgetown University · McCourt School of Public Policy</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-years\">2025 – present</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-desc\">Specializing in program evaluation, causal inference, and applied statistics. Coursework in econometrics, spatial analysis, and evidence-based policy design.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n      <div class=\"tl-dot-col\"><div class=\"tl-dot\" style=\"background:#6ECDC5;\"></div><div class=\"tl-line\"></div></div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"tl-role\">Senior Policy Strategist</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-org\">Mathematica Policy Research</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-years\">2022 – 2024</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-desc\">Led evaluation and strategy engagements for federal health and workforce clients. Managed $4M+ project portfolio and a team of 6 analysts. Produced policy briefs informing HHS and DOL program design.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n      <div class=\"tl-dot-col\"><div class=\"tl-dot\" style=\"background:#8BBFE8;\"></div><div class=\"tl-line\"></div></div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"tl-role\">Program Evaluator</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-org\">Urban Institute</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-years\">2019 – 2022</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-desc\">Designed and conducted mixed-methods evaluations of DOL and HHS grant programs. Co-authored 7 peer-reviewed publications. Developed evaluation frameworks adopted across 3 federal agencies.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"timeline-item\">\n      <div class=\"tl-dot-col\"><div class=\"tl-dot\" style=\"background:#B8D8F8;\"></div></div>\n      <div>\n        <div class=\"tl-role\">Policy Analyst</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-org\">Cook County Dept. of Public Health</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-years\">2016 – 2019</div>\n        <div class=\"tl-desc\">Developed and tracked indicators for community health improvement plan. Coordinated across 12 departments and 40+ community organizations. First role in government after graduate school.</div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Education -->\n<div class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"section-divider\">Education</div>\n  <div class=\"grid-2\">\n    <div style=\"background:#DAEEFF;border-radius:12px;padding:1.2rem;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#2E7DBF;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Current</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;color:#1A3A5C;margin-bottom:0.2rem;\">Master of Public Policy</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#4A6A88;\">Georgetown University · McCourt School</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.78rem;color:#8AA4C0;\">2025 – 2027</div>\n    </div>\n    <div style=\"background:#F7FAFE;border:1px solid #D0DFF0;border-radius:12px;padding:1.2rem;\">\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.72rem;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#8AA4C0;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Undergraduate</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:1rem;font-weight:500;color:#1A3A5C;margin-bottom:0.2rem;\">B.A. Economics &amp; Political Science</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.85rem;color:#4A6A88;\">University of Delhi</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size:0.78rem;color:#8AA4C0;\">2012 – 2016</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n```\n","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"page-hero\">\n  <div class=\"content-section\" style=\"padding-top:0;padding-bottom:0;\">\n    <p class=\"eyebrow\">About</p>\n    <h1 style=\"font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:0.3rem;\">Anurita Sharma</h1>\n    <p style=\"color:#4A6A88;font-size:0.95rem;\">Policy Strategist · Program Manager · Georgetown University</p>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- Bio + S